Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:46.13,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:16.22,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:27.83,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:37.84,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:13.73,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:28.43,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:16.48,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've made a great number of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with your new bond, you've obtained the Hanged Man Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bonds will continue to strengthen through your encounters and conversations,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you gain a deeper understanding of one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I get to see Risette!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Okay, you got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Schedule an interview with the magazine tomorrow at 11:30 PM at our office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:01:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been crazy since she got the lead role for that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A costume check for the movie at 2:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a recording for a radio talk show at 5:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,filming for a commercial at 8:00, and we finish at 4:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Risette! Risette! Risette! {This line continues down through the next 2 lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Risette! Risette! Risette! {This line continues down through the next 2 lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha— Wait! Hey, Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine your fans must be worried because of your sudden hiatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you suffering from any health problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, my health isn't an issue or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it related to your mental health?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you'll be taking your break in Inaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This means Risette is here for real! {This line is showing at the same time next 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Excuse me, but why a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Rise has no further comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe an idol's coming out here! {Same time as line above and below}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll be back after a quick commercial break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This has everything I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqua Balance will revitalize your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Milk? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, isn't that her? {Same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, you take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No way! Isn't that Risette?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've said so sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}did{\i0} give it back to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that strap...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't your grandmother run a traditional tofu shop in Inaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:05:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know when you'll return to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, think we'll run into Rise? {Pretty sure Nanako says 'Rise-chan'}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So are you looking to retire? {Same time as line under}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, you saw her? You saw Rise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't know. {Same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How will you be spending your time? {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool! Was she as cute as she is on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,100)}I haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't Inaba have those unresolved serial murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, we're out of time, {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The best thing about this town was how quiet it was, but it's gotten crazy this past year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but stay tuned for these commercials. {same time as line above}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that I'm the only {\i1}true{\i0} you.{what does this even mean?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for your true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For licensing, go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your Future"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Amagi, you know Rise's family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Marukyu is probably the traditional tofu shop they were referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We carry their tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we went by the tofu shop, we could see Rise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Now isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cases are really linked with the TV, she might be targeted next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like Rise's never been on TV before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but Rise's only connection with the late Ms. Yamano
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,was that they appeared on one or two shows together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With all the fuss about her break, she's the talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To top it all off, she's moving here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. If our assumptions are correct, she fits the criteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadduya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If he goes after Rise,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then the killer is targeting people from this town who show up on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll debunk the theory that he's targeting people related to Ms. Yamano's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Oh, now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still don't know the killer's motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's got a grudge against us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I got a shitload of people who hate my guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Amagi, what about you? You ever piss anyone off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Yukiko! Everyone's done something bad without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, in any case, I have no idea what everyone's done to cause such animosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can ask him about his motives after we catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we should keep an eye on Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, that's Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure? Doesn't she seem kinda different?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 100% sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That chest! Those hips! And her beautiful, thin legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you looking at me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what? I gotta disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie, Jiraiya is Hanamura's Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours is Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chie's is Tomoe. {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you guys taking this seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We are. {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What is Chie's? A "Chie Pet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then should we check out the tofu shop? {same time as line above}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko and I have to run by the Faculty Office, {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chie's is the Chie Pet Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go! {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chie's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, this is for our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't about seeing Rise in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with the excuses already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a bunch of weirdos hanging around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back now after coming all this way to see Risette!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ex-excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see the notice? We're out of tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It-It's really R-Risette!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Rise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you sound so lame?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're the guy from yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You already know each other? No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you come to get some tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Six fried tofu fritters, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice ad lib!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Six fried tofu fritters it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got attitude problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm glad we came. We've cleared our mission for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A job? Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you noticed anything strange lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything strange? Like a stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard of the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that program last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you watch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since I'd heard the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But the girl on TV wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never worn that swimsuit in a promotional video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, my chest isn't that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Down, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The person on that show might get kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard to believe, but we aren't lying or pulling your leg. {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! You're upsetting the neighbors, so beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsumi Kanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, um... Oh right, we're here to get some fried tofu fritters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Adachi from the Inaba PD.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are policemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've already heard, but this area has been dangerous as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you suddenly decide to take a break here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I got tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't mean to scare you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a chance I could get kidnapped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Those three guys just warned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I still have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she's in town anyway, she should've asked our chief to help for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I only came to warn Kujikawa Rise based on my detective's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How could some high school kids who don't even know the situation beat me to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, why are we stalking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We might find the guy who's after Rise if we trail her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes peeled for any suspicious characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones who look suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth are you guys doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You look really suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do deliver everywhere, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave the bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the extra large.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's roast pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I got Tokyo-style noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch my steak over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The other noodles are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here, here! The set's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What's a detective doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima ordered me to—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, I overheard you making an order while doing some legwork for Dojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about timing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, why do we have to eat with a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't eaten yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let me eat my tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That hit the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You little—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave Risette to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, you watch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, dammit! I'm gonna pummel ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! It'll be on the police if the suspect gets hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just your typical Risette-loving civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hardly "typical" after murdering people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Save it for the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo! I've always wanted to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your help in apprehending the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on! Keep up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's all over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The case is solved? Booyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he really was a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really get kidnapped by a wimp like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it safe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see if someone's coming from any direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to dealing with stalkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better if you weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl everyone makes such a fuss over isn't the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Risette, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a fictional character sold to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No one sees the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!{fold cranes, acquire bitches}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I can do it if I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the coast's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It's getting dark out, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You never told me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kujikawa Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard on the news last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Midnight Channel last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I caught a glimpse of her in the store when I passed by this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like the variety show only starts up once they've entered the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we discuss how the person inside the TV could be producing the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be subconsciously showing us their inner thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But then what's up with the fuzzy program that comes on before they go missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be the killer's warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But who is he warning? And why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that we're seeing the killer's thoughts, so it {\i1}looks{\i0} like a warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're seeing who he's targeting next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying it's his fantasies of "I'm gonna attack you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that mean the weirdo from earlier wasn't our guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All we know for sure is that Kujikawa Rise is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kujikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're starting school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm transferring into one of the freshman classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to file the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's for sophomores.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're my senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to show me the ropes, Narukami.{She says "Narukami-Senpai"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just transferred here last April myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't here when I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how they heard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a different route.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like a TV drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't sneak through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As your manager, I simply can't accept your decision to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an idol anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not some puppet who needs someone to micromanage her time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the movie you were just given the lead role for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to force me to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanami has taken your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanami? Mashita Kanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to support Kanami to the best of my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you aren't deceiving yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get involved just for the hell of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.95,0:23:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you aren't careful, you could get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna play, do it elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two fighting again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maru-Q! {She says this like "Maru-Kyun!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a bunch of Risettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.50,0:24:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does this feel so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My glasses, my glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye... forever.
